flowchart TD
    A[Start: hypotheses and EDA findings] --> B[Re-read original confirm and refute criteria]
    B --> C[Map supporting and contradicting evidence]
    C --> D[Rate evidence strength per hypothesis]
    D --> E[Write direct answers to each sub-question]
    E --> F[Separate known facts from interpretation]
    F --> G[List open questions and reframes]
    G --> H[Produce synthesis.md with conclusions]
    H --> I[Checkpoint: proceed to Validation?]
